{"version":1,"entries":{"person_4254071_translations":{"at":1772647160270,"data":{"id":4254071,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чжоу Цянь Сяо","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhou Qianxiao","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhou Qian Xiao","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"周千筱","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"周千筱","primary":false}}]}},"person_2878_translations":{"at":1772647176051,"data":{"id":2878,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Christopher Thomas Howell (born December 7, 1966), usually credited as C. Thomas Howell, is an American actor and film director. He starred in the films The Outsiders as Ponyboy Curtis and in The Hitcher as Jim Halsey. He has appeared in Soul Man, Red Dawn, Secret Admirer, Gettysburg, H. G. Wells' War of the Worlds, The Day the Earth Stopped and Gods and Generals.  Howell was born in the Van Nuys neighborhood of Los Angeles to Christopher N. and Candice Howell. He has three siblings.\n\nHis father worked as a stunt coordinator and rodeo performer. He played the role of the Red Knight in Terry Gilliam’s The Fisher King. As a young boy, Howell wanted to be a stuntman and was a child stunt performer. He was also a rodeo star.\n\nWhen Howell was young, his parents divorced. Howell graduated from Saugus High School in 1984.\n\nIn 1982, Howell made his film debut as Tyler in Steven Spielberg's E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial.\n\nAt the age of 15 in 1981, Howell was cast in Francis Ford Coppola's The Outsiders (1983). Howell played the lead role of Ponyboy Curtis, \"the soulful tagalong greaser through whose eyes we see the events of the 1960s-set film unfold.\" Based on S.E. Hinton's bestselling 1967 novel of the same name,the coming-of-age film went on to become a cult classic. Howell's portrayal of Ponyboy was his breakthrough role, and it earned him a Young Artist Award.\n\nIn 1984, Howell and his Outsiders co-star Patrick Swayze reunited for Grandview, U.S.A. and Red Dawn. Howell also had a pivotal role in Tank (1984). In 1985, he starred in Secret Admirer. After filming The Outsiders, Howell co-starred in his own television series Two Marriages, which ended after four episodes, but letters of support got it back on air. He later expressed disappointment in the series.\n\nHowell was one of two final actors in the running for the lead role of Marty McFly in Back to the Future (1985); the other was Eric Stoltz. Ultimately, Michael J. Fox was cast as Marty after Stoltz was deemed wrong for the part. In 1986, Howell was a hitchhiker's target in the film The Hitcher. He also starred in the sequel, which was released in 2003. In 1986, Howell starred in Soul Man, a film in which Howell appears in Blackface. Rounding out the 1980s , Howell played the young Arturo Toscanini in Franco Zeffirelli's 1988 film Young Toscanini.","name":"C. Thomas Howell","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Christopher Thomas Howell (* 7. Dezember 1966 in Los Angeles, Kalifornien) ist ein US-amerikanischer Schauspieler und Filmregisseur.\n\nAls Schauspieler trat er Anfang der 1980er Jahre in Erscheinung und spielte Rollen in den Kinohits E.T. und Die Outsider. Diese Auftritte ließen ihn zu einem Teeniestar und Mitglied des Brat Packs werden.\n\nAls Erwachsener tritt er mittlerweile hauptsächlich in Gastrollen in Fernsehserien wie Emergency Room auf und ist Mitbesitzer der Produktionsfirma Buckwheat Films.\n\nHowell ist auch als Regisseur aktiv, sein Debüt gab er 1995 mit dem Film Im Netz der Verführung (Originaltitel: Hourglass). Hierfür verfasste er auch erstmals ein Drehbuch. Im darauffolgenden Jahr inszenierte er die Actionfilme The Big Fall – Im Fadenkreuz des Todes sowie Pure Danger – Fluchtpunkt L.A. Im Jahr 2008 entstand mit Krieg der Welten 2 – Die nächste Angriffswelle sein vierter Film als Regisseur. Im Anschluss inszenierte er Der Tag an dem die Erde stillstand 2 – Angriff der Roboter, 2009 drehte er The Land That Time Forgot. In all diesen Produktionen übernahm Howell auch die jeweilige Hauptrolle. Zuletzt war er als Regisseur an The Genesis Code (2010) beteiligt.\n\nSeit 2009 spielte er in der Polizei-Serie Southland den Officer Billy „Dewey“ Dudek. In den ersten vier Staffeln wirkte er bis 2012 in 17 Folgen wiederkehrend als Nebendarsteller, in der fünften und letzten Staffel gehörte Howell zum Hauptcast der Serie.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"C·湯瑪斯·哈威爾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克里斯托弗·托马斯·豪威尔（Christopher Thomas Howell，1966 年 12 月 7 日出生），通常被称为 C. 托马斯·豪威尔，是一位美国演员和电影导演。他在电影《局外人》中饰演小马仔柯蒂斯，在《杀手》中饰演吉姆·哈尔西。他曾出演过《灵魂人》、《红色黎明》、《秘密崇拜者》、《葛底斯堡》、《HG 威尔斯的世界大战》、《地球停止的那一天》和《众神与将军》。他计划出现在2012年的《超凡蜘蛛侠》中。","name":"克里斯托弗·托马斯·豪威尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克里斯託弗·託馬斯·豪威爾（Christopher Thomas Howell，1966 年 12 月 7 日出生），通常被稱為 C. 託馬斯·豪威爾，是一位美國演員和電影導演。他在電影《局外人》中飾演小馬仔柯蒂斯，在《躁爸爸狂媽媽》中飾演吉姆·哈爾西。他曾出演過《靈魂人》、《紅色黎明》、《秘密崇拜者》、《葛底斯堡》、《HG 威爾斯的世界大戰》、《地球停止的那一天》和《眾神與將軍》。他計劃出現在 2012 年的《蜘蛛俠：驚世現新》中。","name":"C·湯瑪斯·哈威爾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ｃ・トーマス・ハウエル","primary":false}}]}},"tv_276083_credits":{"at":1772647185220,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gende