reer, he has become one of the most beloved voices in Chinese animation and drama, celebrated for his vocal range, emotional depth, and versatility.\n\nAjie is best known for portraying iconic characters such as Wei Wuxian in The Founder of Diabolism and Ye Xiu in The King's Avatar. Beyond voice acting, he also works as an ADR supervisor (voice direction) in various productions, showcasing his technical and artistic mastery in the field.","name":"Ajie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿杰是中国内地的男性配音演员、配音导演，本名张杰。\n\n北京圈知名配音演员，729声工场的创始人。\n\n声线华丽，配翩翩佳公子一类的男性角色非常贴合，且有自己的特色。\n\n本科专业是旅游英语，毕业以后做过一阵子导游，后发现自己心底里还是最爱配音，于是走上了配音道路。先是加入网络社团声优之翼（现声创联盟），后与X-ray，老房等人成立了网络配音社团729配音组。2006年开始踏入配音行业。","name":"阿杰","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿傑","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"А Цзе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Jie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿傑是中國內地的男性配音演員、配音導演，本名張傑。\n\n北京圈知名配音演員，729 聲工場的創始人。\n\n聲線華麗，配翩翩佳公子一類的男性角色非常貼合，且有自己的特色。\n\n本科專業是旅遊英語，畢業以後做過一陣子導遊，後發現自己心底裏還是最愛配音，於是走上了配音道路。先是加入網絡社團聲優之翼（現聲創聯盟），後與 X - ray，老房等人成立了網絡配音社團 729 配音組。2006 年開始踏入配音行業。","name":"阿傑","primary":false}}]}},"tv_15673_keywords":{"at":1772647196720,"data":{"id":15673,"results":[]}},"person_2722648_translations":{"at":1772647205732,"data":{"id":2722648,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"龟娘，本名杜晴晴。1991年4月1日出生，歌手、配音演员、游戏解说。\n\n代表作有广播剧《楼兰》、童话广播剧《英雄巴利》、《哀思》等。代表角色包括《鬼灭之刃》蝴蝶忍、《妖怪名单》郭双、《我为歌狂之旋律重启》林清儿、《原神》珊瑚宫心海、《明日方舟》灰毫等。","name":"杜晴晴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Du Qingqing","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Qingqing Du","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ду Циньцинь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"龜娘，本名杜晴晴。1991 年 4 月 1 日出生，歌手、配音演員、遊戲解説。\n\n代表作有廣播劇《樓蘭》、童話廣播劇《英雄巴利》、《哀思》等。代表角色包括《鬼滅之刃》蝴蝶忍、《妖怪名單》郭雙、《我為歌狂之旋律重啟》林清兒、《原神》珊瑚宮心海、《明日方舟》灰毫等。","name":"杜晴晴","primary":false}}]}},"person_116474_translations":{"at":1772647211162,"data":{"id":116474,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kevin Alejandro is an American actor.","name":"Kevin Alejandro","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kevin Michael Alejandro (7 de abril de 1976), es un actor estadounidense.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"케빈 알레한드로","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凱文·亞歷杭德羅","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凯文·亚历杭德罗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кевин Алехандро","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"